	//About Us
	section.sectioon.section-lg.bg-default.bg-custom-gray#about
		.container
			.row.row-50.justify-content-lg-between

				.col-lg-6
					h6.subtitle-section.text-primary.wow.fadeInLeft(data-wow-delay='.1s') About us
					h2.title-section.block-1.wow.fadeInLeft(data-wow-delay='.2s') We Turn Ideas Into Reality
					p.text-gray-800.wow.fadeInLeft(data-wow-delay='.3s') We apply innovative design solutions to enhance people’s residential well-being and to help workplaces succeed & achieve more in the comfortable environments!
					p.font-weight-light.wow.fadeInLeft(data-wow-delay='.4s') All our team collaborates with our clients, across all of our 3 offices, which are located throughout the US. Our mission is to implement the outstanding design ideas and solutions for any project we’re working on. During that process, we carefully combine client’s guidelines, technical possibilities as well as the environmental issues. Engineering and interior design solutions that we deliver are usually born after a collaborative process.
					.row.row-40.text-center.text-lg-left.box-nina-wrapper
						.col-sm-4.box-nina.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-delay='.2s')
							.box-nina-icon
								span.icon.icon-lg.text-gray-800.linearicons-apartment
							h6.box-nina-title: a(href='#') Architecture
						.col-sm-4.box-nina.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-delay='.2s')
